SUMMARY:Crafting Circle
DESCRIPTION:Do you do a handicraft? Get together with your fellow TNTers for 2 hours of crafting. Bring your knitting\, needlepoint\, embroidery\, crochet\, lace-making\, cross-stitch\, or whatever handicraft you are working on and join us for schmoozing\, learning from each other and community. We meet once a month on a Sunday afternoon at TNT. Email hello@nertamid.org for more information. 
URL:https://nertamid.org/event/crafting-circle-2/
LOCATION:NJ
CATEGORIES:General
END:VEVENT
