DESCRIPTION:Through song\, ritual\, and reflection\, we will share a meaningful Seder experience followed by a catered dinner from Marcel’s \n Bakery. Women and teen girls are warmly invited to attend together for an evening of connection\, tradition\, and shared voices. \n  \nRSVP is required by following this link\nQuestions? Contact Cantor Greenberg cantor@nertamid.org
